<script>
    function setEdition(target) {
        // set cookie for default edition
        //document.cookie ="myEdition="+target+"; expires=Fri, 1 Jan 2038 01:23:45 GMT; path=/";
        var days=90;
        var date = new Date();
        date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
        var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
        var currentTime = (new Date).getTime();
        document.cookie = "editionPostpone="+currentTime+expires+"; path=/";

		ga('send', 'event', 'outbound', 'click',target+'.investing.com');
		setTimeout('document.location = "http://'+ target +'.investing.com?ref=www"', 500);
	}

    function postponeEdition(days) {
        if (days!=14) days=1;
        //$('#editionLoading').removeClass("displayNone").addClass("inlineblock");
        // set cookie for days not to show bar again
        //change time from 7 days to 14 (2 weeks), Gil Palikaras, JIRA-26314
        var date = new Date();
        date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
        var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
        var currentTime = (new Date).getTime();
        document.cookie = "editionPostpone="+currentTime+expires+"; path=/";
        closeTopAlert();
    }
    function closeTopAlert(){
        $('#topAlertBarContainer').fadeOut('fast');
    }

    $(document).ready (function(){
                //openTopAlert(2000);
            });
</script>			<!-- /GEO POPUP -->

<script type="text/javascript">
window.Adomik = window.Adomik || {};
    Adomik.randomAdGroup = function() {
    var rand = Math.random();
    switch (false) {
    case !(rand < 0.09): return "ad_ex" + (Math.floor(100 * rand));
    case !(rand < 0.10): return "ad_bc";
    default: return "ad_opt";
    }
};
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">

	function onBigX() {
		$('#theBigX').fadeOut('fast');

		// click tracking issue 27402
		ga('create', 'UA-2555300-55', 'auto', {name: 'allSitesTracker'});
		ga('send', 'event', 'Homepage Billboard', 'X-Close Billboard');
		////////////////////////////////

		$('.midHeader').animate({
			height: '90px'
		},200 );
		googletag.cmd.push(function() {
			googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Leaderboard_Default', [[728, 90], [970, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
			googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1'); });
		});
		$('#div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').hide();
		$('#div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').show();
	};

	function checkBigAd() {
		var cname =getCookie("show_big_billboard1");
		if( true && !cname && true) {
			setCookie('show_big_billboard1','true', 0.0833333333333333); //0.0416666666666667 for 1 hour, 0.125 for three hours, 0.00625 for three minutes and so on

			$('.midHeader').height('250px');
			$('#div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').show();
			$('#div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').hide();
			$('#theBigX').show();
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Billboard_Default',  [970, 250] , 'div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
				googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6'); });
			});
		} else {
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Leaderboard_Default', [[728, 90], [970, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
				googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1'); });
			});
		}
	}

</script>

	    <script type="text/javascript">
function changeFindABrokerTabContent(childObj)
{
	$(childObj).unbind('click');
	$(childObj).addClass('selected').siblings().each(function(){
		if($(this).is('.selected')) {
			$(this).bind('click',function()
					{ changeFindABrokerTabContent(this); }
			);
		}
		$(this).removeClass('selected');
	});
	var clickedtab = $(childObj).attr('tab');
	$('#findABroker_html').html("<br><br><br><br><br><br>").addClass('loading-responsive');
	$.get('/ads/FABAjax',
			{activetab: clickedtab}
	, function(data)
	{ $('#findABroker_html').removeClass('loading-responsive').html(data); }
	);
}
</script>

	function checkAds(){

		function isIE() {
			var ua = window.navigator.userAgent;
			var trident = ua.indexOf('Trident/');
			var edge = ua.indexOf('Edge/');
			var msie = ua.indexOf('MSIE ');
			return Math.max(msie,edge,trident)>0;

		}

		var isIE = isIE();
		var isChrome = /Chrome/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Google Inc/.test(navigator.vendor) && !isIE;
		var isFireFox = /Firefox/.test(navigator.userAgent);
		var isSafari = /Safari/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Apple Computer/.test(navigator.vendor);
		var isOneOfThoseBrowsers = [isIE,isChrome,isFireFox,isSafari].indexOf(true)>-1;

        		ga('allSitesTracker.set', 'dimension22', '1_Blk_No');
        		setCookie('adbBLk',1,-1000);
    		}  
    		
    	}else{

    	    b = 1;
            $('#TopTextAd').css('display','flex');

			if(isOneOfThoseBrowsers) {
				setCookie('adbBLk',1,1000,'/');
				ga('allSitesTracker.set', 'dimension21', '1_Blk_Yes');
				 
									ga('allSitesTracker.set', 'dimension24', '1_AdBlkPopup');
							}
    	}
		
		$.ajax({
		    url: "/jp.php?b="+b+"&k=ZDVhNGU7NDk-bWxjZzc3YWA2NG5hY2VhMzNvZDAzYD8wYzcyZzcyYmY2aTVnO2Y-Y2IzMWVlMWMxM2BkNzRnZ2R7YShldDQ9PjpsYWc2NzZgLzQ5YTllJTNnbyQwd2AoMGk3Imd_MmRmbmlo&d=1",

function trackSignUpGAEvent(eventName, eventParam) {
			switch (eventName) {
			case 'Header button':
			case 'Exit Signup':
			case 'Facebook':
			case 'Google+':
			case 'Email':
			case 'Register':
			case 'Send code':
			case 'Complete SMS':
				if (eventParam) {
					ga('send', 'event', 'Signup', eventName, eventParam);
				} else {
					ga('send', 'event', 'Signup', eventName);
				}
		}
	}

        var pageToTrack= '/' + eventName + '.html';
        ga('registrationTracker.send', 'pageview', pageToTrack);
        ga('registrationTracker.send', 'event', 'click', eventName);
        
    }

<script>
//disabled is a temporary argument for testing purposes 
var BoxesEvents = function($,ga,disabled)
{
	var e_stack = []; //each event is pushed to this stack
	//this objcet links urls to event types
    var boxes = {"side_central_banks":"centralbanks","webmaster_tools":"wmt","Most_Popular_News":"mostpop","broker_promotions":"sb_promotions","marketMoversBoxWrapper":"sb_marketmovers","QBS_2_inner":"sb_indices","QBS_3_inner":"sb_commodities","QBS_1_inner":"sb_forex","QBS_4_inner":"sb_bonds","TSB_1_inner":"tsb_fx","TSB_2_inner":"tsb_commodities","TSB_3_inner":"tsb_indices","TSB_4_inner":"tsb_stocks"};

    var resume_click_event = function(ev)
    {
    	if (ev['link']==='') {return;}
        window.location.href = ev['link'];
    }
    
    
	var register_events = function()
	{
	    for (var id in boxes)
	    {
		    (function(id){
			    var _$b = $('#'+id);
			    if (_$b.length < 1) {return;}
			    
			    //box click event
			    _$b.mouseup(function(e){
					if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
					var middleMouse = e.button === 1;
				    if (!middleMouse) {e.preventDefault();}
				    var box_event = boxes[id];
				    e_stack.push({'event':box_event,'link':''});
				    var ce = null; //current event 
				    //function creator
				    var callbackCreate = function(data) {return function() {resume_click_event(data);}}
		            var hitCallback = null;
		            
				    while(ce = e_stack.pop())
				    {
						if (ce['link'].substr(0,10) === "javascript") {continue;}//if the link is javascript call ignore it
						hitCallback = middleMouse ? function(){} : callbackCreate(ce);
				    	//if a link with no event do nothing
					    if (ce['event'] == '') {hitCallback(); return true;}
						
				    					        window.ga('t0.send',{
                            'hitType': 'event',          
                            'eventCategory': 'side-box-events',
                            'eventAction': ce['event'], 
                            'eventValue' : 1,
                            'hitCallback': hitCallback //resume click event
				            }
				        );
				        //fallback if ga doesn't work
				        window.setTimeout(hitCallback,1500);
				    }
				    return middleMouse;
			    });
			    
			    //link event 
                _$b.on('mouseup','a',function(e){
					if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
                	e.preventDefault();
					var url = this.getAttribute('href');
					var event = this.getAttribute('data-gae');
					e_stack.push({'event':'','link':url});
					if (event)
					{
						e_stack.pop();
						e_stack.push({'event':event,'link':url});
					} 
				  });
    	        
		    })(id);
	    }		   	
	};
	
    var init = function()
    {
        if (disabled) {return;}
        if (typeof $ !== 'function') {return;}
        if (typeof ga !== 'function') {return;}
        register_events();
    }();
}(window.jQuery,window.ga,false);
</script>
<script>
	var marketLinksGA = function()
	{
		var createGAlinkEvent = function(linkLabel)
		{
			return function(e)
			{
				if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
				var middleMouse = e.button === 1;
				var enableCallback = true;
				var url = this.getAttribute('href');
				var callbackCreate = function(url) {return function() {window.location.href = url;};};
				var callback = function() {};
				
				enableCallback = this.hasAttribute('href') && !middleMouse;
				if (enableCallback) {e.preventDefault();}
				if (enableCallback) {callback = callbackCreate(url);}
				
				window.ga('t0.send',{
					'hitType': 'event',          
					'eventCategory': 'markets-links',
					'eventAction': 'click', 
					'eventLabel': linkLabel, 
					'eventValue' : 1,
					'hitCallback': callback
					}
				);
		
				//fallback incase google callback doesn't work
				window.setTimeout(callback,1500);
		
				return !enableCallback;
			};
		};
		
		var init = function()
		{
			//add action with google analytics
			$("#navRealTime > a").click(createGAlinkEvent('markets-top-navigation'));
			$("#markets_subnav_link").click(createGAlinkEvent('markets-popular'));
		}();

			$(document).ready(function (e) {
				var quotes = [
				'S&P 500','Nasdaq Composite','Gold','Crude Oil','EUR/USD','USD/JPY','US 10Y Yield',
				'EUR/USD 2nd','GBP/USD','USD/JPY 2nd','USD/CHF','AUD/USD','USD/CAD','BTC/USD',
				'Dow 30','S&P 500 2nd','Nasdaq 100','DAX','FTSE 100','Nikkei 225','Hang Seng'
				];

				$('.quotesBarContentCellTop').click(function (e) {
					e.preventDefault(); // redirect after the following code
					var reDirectUrl =$('a',this).attr('href');
					var ulIdx = $(this).closest('ul').index()-1;
					var liIdx = $(this).closest('li').index();
					var quoteIdx = ulIdx*7+liIdx;
					if (typeof ga) {
					ga('send', 'event', quotes[quoteIdx], 'Click', 'HP Quotes Bar'); // replace to ga after Netta's approval.

					}
					if(reDirectUrl && reDirectUrl.length){
					setTimeout(function (e) {location.href=reDirectUrl;return;}, 100);
					}
					return false;
				});
			});





			}();
</script>

<script>

<script>
    function setEdition(target) {
        // set cookie for default edition
        //document.cookie ="myEdition="+target+"; expires=Fri, 1 Jan 2038 01:23:45 GMT; path=/";
        var days=90;
        var date = new Date();
        date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
        var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
        var currentTime = (new Date).getTime();
        document.cookie = "editionPostpone="+currentTime+expires+"; path=/";

		ga('send', 'event', 'outbound', 'click',target+'.investing.com');
		setTimeout('document.location = "http://'+ target +'.investing.com?ref=www"', 500);
	}

    function postponeEdition(days) {
        if (days!=14) days=1;
        //$('#editionLoading').removeClass("displayNone").addClass("inlineblock");
        // set cookie for days not to show bar again
        //change time from 7 days to 14 (2 weeks), Gil Palikaras, JIRA-26314
        var date = new Date();
        date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
        var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
        var currentTime = (new Date).getTime();
        document.cookie = "editionPostpone="+currentTime+expires+"; path=/";
        closeTopAlert();
    }
    function closeTopAlert(){
        $('#topAlertBarContainer').fadeOut('fast');
    }

    $(document).ready (function(){
                //openTopAlert(2000);
            });
</script>			<!-- /GEO POPUP -->

    Adomik.randomAdGroup = function() {
    var rand = Math.random();
    switch (false) {
    case !(rand < 0.09): return "ad_ex" + (Math.floor(100 * rand));
    case !(rand < 0.10): return "ad_bc";
    default: return "ad_opt";
    }
};

<script type="text/javascript">

	function onBigX() {
		$('#theBigX').fadeOut('fast');

		// click tracking issue 27402
		ga('create', 'UA-2555300-55', 'auto', {name: 'allSitesTracker'});
		ga('send', 'event', 'Homepage Billboard', 'X-Close Billboard');
		////////////////////////////////

		$('.midHeader').animate({
			height: '90px'
		},200 );
		googletag.cmd.push(function() {
			googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Leaderboard_Default', [[728, 90], [970, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
			googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1'); });
		});
		$('#div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').hide();
		$('#div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').show();
	};

	function checkBigAd() {
		var cname =getCookie("show_big_billboard1");
		if( true && !cname && true) {
			setCookie('show_big_billboard1','true', 0.0833333333333333); //0.0416666666666667 for 1 hour, 0.125 for three hours, 0.00625 for three minutes and so on

			$('.midHeader').height('250px');
			$('#div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').show();
			$('#div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').hide();
			$('#theBigX').show();
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Billboard_Default',  [970, 250] , 'div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
				googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6'); });
			});
		} else {
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Leaderboard_Default', [[728, 90], [970, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
				googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1'); });
			});
		}
	}

</script>

	    <script type="text/javascript">
function changeFindABrokerTabContent(childObj)
{
	$(childObj).unbind('click');
	$(childObj).addClass('selected').siblings().each(function(){
		if($(this).is('.selected')) {
			$(this).bind('click',function()
					{ changeFindABrokerTabContent(this); }
			);
		}
		$(this).removeClass('selected');
	});
	var clickedtab = $(childObj).attr('tab');
	$('#findABroker_html').html("<br><br><br><br><br><br>").addClass('loading-responsive');
	$.get('/ads/FABAjax',
			{activetab: clickedtab}
	, function(data)
	{ $('#findABroker_html').removeClass('loading-responsive').html(data); }
	);
}
</script>

	function checkAds(){

		function isIE() {
			var ua = window.navigator.userAgent;
			var trident = ua.indexOf('Trident/');
			var edge = ua.indexOf('Edge/');
			var msie = ua.indexOf('MSIE ');
			return Math.max(msie,edge,trident)>0;

		}

		var isIE = isIE();
		var isChrome = /Chrome/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Google Inc/.test(navigator.vendor) && !isIE;
		var isFireFox = /Firefox/.test(navigator.userAgent);
		var isSafari = /Safari/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Apple Computer/.test(navigator.vendor);
		var isOneOfThoseBrowsers = [isIE,isChrome,isFireFox,isSafari].indexOf(true)>-1;

		var b = 2;

		//var hasAdsenseBlock = !!$('#adsense').length;
		//var hasShadowDom = (!!$("html")[0].shadowRoot);
		//var headerIsShown = ($(".midHeader").height() > 0 && $(".midHeader").css('display') !== 'none');

	    		  
		if (window.google_ad_status == 1){

    		var adbBlk = getCookie('adbBLk');
    		if(isOneOfThoseBrowsers && adbBlk>0){
        		ga('allSitesTracker.set', 'dimension22', '1_Blk_No');
        		setCookie('adbBLk',1,-1000);
    		}  
    		
    	}else{

    	    b = 1;
            $('#TopTextAd').css('display','flex');

			if(isOneOfThoseBrowsers) {
				setCookie('adbBLk',1,1000,'/');
				ga('allSitesTracker.set', 'dimension21', '1_Blk_Yes');
				 
									ga('allSitesTracker.set', 'dimension24', '1_AdBlkPopup');
							}
    	}
		
		$.ajax({
		    url: "/jp.php?b="+b+"&k=ZDVhNGU7NDk-bWxjZzc3YWA2NG5hY2VhMzNvZDAzYD8wYzcyZzcyYmY2aTVnO2Y-Y2IzMWVlMWMxM2BkNzRnZ2R7YShldDQ9PjpsYWc2NzZgLzQ5YTllJTNnbyQwd2AoMGk3Imd_MmRmbmlo&d=1",

function trackSignUpGAEvent(eventName, eventParam) {
			switch (eventName) {
			case 'Header button':
			case 'Exit Signup':
			case 'Facebook':
			case 'Google+':
			case 'Email':
			case 'Register':
			case 'Send code':
			case 'Complete SMS':
				if (eventParam) {
					ga('send', 'event', 'Signup', eventName, eventParam);
				} else {
					ga('send', 'event', 'Signup', eventName);
				}
		}
	}

    function trackGAEvent(eventName){
        var pageToTrack= '/' + eventName + '.html';
        ga('registrationTracker.send', 'pageview', pageToTrack);
        ga('registrationTracker.send', 'event', 'click', eventName);
        
    }

<script>
//disabled is a temporary argument for testing purposes 
var BoxesEvents = function($,ga,disabled)
{
	var e_stack = []; //each event is pushed to this stack
	//this objcet links urls to event types
    var boxes = {"side_central_banks":"centralbanks","webmaster_tools":"wmt","Most_Popular_News":"mostpop","broker_promotions":"sb_promotions","marketMoversBoxWrapper":"sb_marketmovers","QBS_2_inner":"sb_indices","QBS_3_inner":"sb_commodities","QBS_1_inner":"sb_forex","QBS_4_inner":"sb_bonds","TSB_1_inner":"tsb_fx","TSB_2_inner":"tsb_commodities","TSB_3_inner":"tsb_indices","TSB_4_inner":"tsb_stocks"};

    var resume_click_event = function(ev)
    {
    	if (ev['link']==='') {return;}
        window.location.href = ev['link'];
    }
    
    
	var register_events = function()
	{
	    for (var id in boxes)
	    {
		    (function(id){
			    var _$b = $('#'+id);
			    if (_$b.length < 1) {return;}
			    
			    //box click event
			    _$b.mouseup(function(e){
					if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
					var middleMouse = e.button === 1;
				    if (!middleMouse) {e.preventDefault();}
				    var box_event = boxes[id];
				    e_stack.push({'event':box_event,'link':''});
				    var ce = null; //current event 
				    //function creator
				    var callbackCreate = function(data) {return function() {resume_click_event(data);}}
		            var hitCallback = null;
		            
				    while(ce = e_stack.pop())
				    {
						if (ce['link'].substr(0,10) === "javascript") {continue;}//if the link is javascript call ignore it
						hitCallback = middleMouse ? function(){} : callbackCreate(ce);
				    	//if a link with no event do nothing
					    if (ce['event'] == '') {hitCallback(); return true;}
						
				    					        window.ga('t0.send',{
                            'hitType': 'event',          
                            'eventCategory': 'side-box-events',
                            'eventAction': ce['event'], 
                            'eventValue' : 1,
                            'hitCallback': hitCallback //resume click event
				            }
				        );
				        //fallback if ga doesn't work
				        window.setTimeout(hitCallback,1500);
				    }
				    return middleMouse;
			    });
			    
			    //link event 
                _$b.on('mouseup','a',function(e){
					if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
                	e.preventDefault();
					var url = this.getAttribute('href');
					var event = this.getAttribute('data-gae');
					e_stack.push({'event':'','link':url});
					if (event)
					{
						e_stack.pop();
						e_stack.push({'event':event,'link':url});
					} 
				  });
    	        
		    })(id);
	    }		   	
	};
	
    var init = function()
    {
        if (disabled) {return;}
        if (typeof $ !== 'function') {return;}
        if (typeof ga !== 'function') {return;}
        register_events();
    }();
}(window.jQuery,window.ga,false);
</script>
<script>
	var marketLinksGA = function()
	{
		var createGAlinkEvent = function(linkLabel)
		{
			return function(e)
			{
				if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
				var middleMouse = e.button === 1;
				var enableCallback = true;
				var url = this.getAttribute('href');
				var callbackCreate = function(url) {return function() {window.location.href = url;};};
				var callback = function() {};
				
				enableCallback = this.hasAttribute('href') && !middleMouse;
				if (enableCallback) {e.preventDefault();}
				if (enableCallback) {callback = callbackCreate(url);}
				
				window.ga('t0.send',{
					'hitType': 'event',          
					'eventCategory': 'markets-links',
					'eventAction': 'click', 
					'eventLabel': linkLabel, 
					'eventValue' : 1,
					'hitCallback': callback
					}
				);
		
				//fallback incase google callback doesn't work
				window.setTimeout(callback,1500);
		
				return !enableCallback;
			};
		};
		
		var init = function()
		{
			//add action with google analytics
			$("#navRealTime > a").click(createGAlinkEvent('markets-top-navigation'));
			$("#markets_subnav_link").click(createGAlinkEvent('markets-popular'));
		}();

			$(document).ready(function (e) {
				var quotes = [
				'S&P 500','Nasdaq Composite','Gold','Crude Oil','EUR/USD','USD/JPY','US 10Y Yield',
				'EUR/USD 2nd','GBP/USD','USD/JPY 2nd','USD/CHF','AUD/USD','USD/CAD','BTC/USD',
				'Dow 30','S&P 500 2nd','Nasdaq 100','DAX','FTSE 100','Nikkei 225','Hang Seng'
				];

				$('.quotesBarContentCellTop').click(function (e) {
					e.preventDefault(); // redirect after the following code
					var reDirectUrl =$('a',this).attr('href');
					var ulIdx = $(this).closest('ul').index()-1;
					var liIdx = $(this).closest('li').index();
					var quoteIdx = ulIdx*7+liIdx;
					if (typeof ga) {
					ga('send', 'event', quotes[quoteIdx], 'Click', 'HP Quotes Bar'); // replace to ga after Netta's approval.

					}
					if(reDirectUrl && reDirectUrl.length){
					setTimeout(function (e) {location.href=reDirectUrl;return;}, 100);
					}
					return false;
				});
			});





			}();
</script>

    <div class="popupInnerWrapper">
        <div class="header"><span><i class="ceFlags China"></i></span><span class="chooseEditionHeaderText">跳转到中文版</span><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="bugCloseIcon" onclick="postponeEdition(14)"></a> </div>

            您更倾向于浏览Investing.com的<span class="bold">中文</span>版吗？        </div>
        <div class="topPortfolioFooter">
            <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="postponeEdition(14)" alt="不，谢谢" class="newBtn LightGray noIcon">不，谢谢</a><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="setEdition(&quot;cn&quot;)" alt="是，跳转至中文站" class="newBtn LightGray noIcon">是，跳转至中文站</a>        </div>
    </div>

<script>
    function setEdition(target) {
        // set cookie for default edition
        //document.cookie ="myEdition="+target+"; expires=Fri, 1 Jan 2038 01:23:45 GMT; path=/";
        var days=90;
        var date = new Date();
        date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
        var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
        var currentTime = (new Date).getTime();
        document.cookie = "editionPostpone="+currentTime+expires+"; path=/";

		ga('send', 'event', 'outbound', 'click',target+'.investing.com');
		setTimeout('document.location = "http://'+ target +'.investing.com?ref=www"', 500);
	}

    function postponeEdition(days) {
        if (days!=14) days=1;
        //$('#editionLoading').removeClass("displayNone").addClass("inlineblock");
        // set cookie for days not to show bar again
        //change time from 7 days to 14 (2 weeks), Gil Palikaras, JIRA-26314
        var date = new Date();
        date.setTime(date.getTime()+(days*24*60*60*1000));
        var expires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
        var currentTime = (new Date).getTime();
        document.cookie = "editionPostpone="+currentTime+expires+"; path=/";
        closeTopAlert();
    }
    function closeTopAlert(){
        $('#topAlertBarContainer').fadeOut('fast');
    }

    $(document).ready (function(){
                //openTopAlert(2000);
            });
</script>			<!-- /GEO POPUP -->
		</div>
	</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
window.Adomik = window.Adomik || {};
    Adomik.randomAdGroup = function() {
    var rand = Math.random();
    switch (false) {
    case !(rand < 0.09): return "ad_ex" + (Math.floor(100 * rand));
    case !(rand < 0.10): return "ad_bc";
    default: return "ad_opt";
    }
};
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">

	function onBigX() {
		$('#theBigX').fadeOut('fast');

		// click tracking issue 27402
		ga('create', 'UA-2555300-55', 'auto', {name: 'allSitesTracker'});
		ga('send', 'event', 'Homepage Billboard', 'X-Close Billboard');
		////////////////////////////////

		$('.midHeader').animate({
			height: '90px'
		},200 );
		googletag.cmd.push(function() {
			googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Leaderboard_Default', [[728, 90], [970, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
			googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1'); });
		});
		$('#div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').hide();
		$('#div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').show();
	};

	function checkBigAd() {
		var cname =getCookie("show_big_billboard1");
		if( true && !cname && true) {
			setCookie('show_big_billboard1','true', 0.0833333333333333); //0.0416666666666667 for 1 hour, 0.125 for three hours, 0.00625 for three minutes and so on

			$('.midHeader').height('250px');
			$('#div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').show();
			$('#div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').hide();
			$('#theBigX').show();
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Billboard_Default',  [970, 250] , 'div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
				googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1441189641022-6'); });
			});
		} else {
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				googletag.defineSlot('/6938/FP_EN_site/FP_EN_Leaderboard_Default', [[728, 90], [970, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1').setTargeting('ad_group', Adomik.randomAdGroup()).addService(googletag.pubads());
				googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1370187203350-head1'); });
			});
		}
	}

</script>

	    <script type="text/javascript">
function changeFindABrokerTabContent(childObj)
{
	$(childObj).unbind('click');
	$(childObj).addClass('selected').siblings().each(function(){
		if($(this).is('.selected')) {
			$(this).bind('click',function()
					{ changeFindABrokerTabContent(this); }
			);
		}
		$(this).removeClass('selected');
	});
	var clickedtab = $(childObj).attr('tab');
	$('#findABroker_html').html("<br><br><br><br><br><br>").addClass('loading-responsive');
	$.get('/ads/FABAjax',
			{activetab: clickedtab}
	, function(data)
	{ $('#findABroker_html').removeClass('loading-responsive').html(data); }
	);
}
</script>

	function checkAds(){

		function isIE() {
			var ua = window.navigator.userAgent;
			var trident = ua.indexOf('Trident/');
			var edge = ua.indexOf('Edge/');
			var msie = ua.indexOf('MSIE ');
			return Math.max(msie,edge,trident)>0;

		}

		var isIE = isIE();
		var isChrome = /Chrome/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Google Inc/.test(navigator.vendor) && !isIE;
		var isFireFox = /Firefox/.test(navigator.userAgent);
		var isSafari = /Safari/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Apple Computer/.test(navigator.vendor);
		var isOneOfThoseBrowsers = [isIE,isChrome,isFireFox,isSafari].indexOf(true)>-1;

    	}else{

		    }
		});
    	
    } 

	ga('allSitesTracker.send', 'pageview');
	
	ga('create', 'UA-2555300-55', 'auto', {'name': 'allSitesTracker'});	ga('create', 'UA-2555300-1', 'investing.com');
function trackSignUpGAEvent(eventName, eventParam) {
			switch (eventName) {
			case 'Header button':
			case 'Exit Signup':
			case 'Facebook':
			case 'Google+':
			case 'Email':
			case 'Register':
			case 'Send code':
			case 'Complete SMS':
				if (eventParam) {
					ga('send', 'event', 'Signup', eventName, eventParam);
				} else {
					ga('send', 'event', 'Signup', eventName);
				}
		}
	}
	<!--End Adblock Check-->

    ga('create', 'UA-2555300-1', 'auto', {'name': 'registrationTracker'});
    function trackGAEvent(eventName){
        var pageToTrack= '/' + eventName + '.html';
        ga('registrationTracker.send', 'pageview', pageToTrack);
        ga('registrationTracker.send', 'event', 'click', eventName);
        
    }


</script>
    
    

 
<script>
//disabled is a temporary argument for testing purposes 
var BoxesEvents = function($,ga,disabled)
{
	var e_stack = []; //each event is pushed to this stack
	//this objcet links urls to event types
    var boxes = {"side_central_banks":"centralbanks","webmaster_tools":"wmt","Most_Popular_News":"mostpop","broker_promotions":"sb_promotions","marketMoversBoxWrapper":"sb_marketmovers","QBS_2_inner":"sb_indices","QBS_3_inner":"sb_commodities","QBS_1_inner":"sb_forex","QBS_4_inner":"sb_bonds","TSB_1_inner":"tsb_fx","TSB_2_inner":"tsb_commodities","TSB_3_inner":"tsb_indices","TSB_4_inner":"tsb_stocks"};

    var resume_click_event = function(ev)
    {
    	if (ev['link']==='') {return;}
        window.location.href = ev['link'];
    }
    
    
	var register_events = function()
	{
	    for (var id in boxes)
	    {
		    (function(id){
			    var _$b = $('#'+id);
			    if (_$b.length < 1) {return;}
			    
			    //box click event
			    _$b.mouseup(function(e){
					if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
					var middleMouse = e.button === 1;
				    if (!middleMouse) {e.preventDefault();}
				    var box_event = boxes[id];
				    e_stack.push({'event':box_event,'link':''});
				    var ce = null; //current event 
				    //function creator
				    var callbackCreate = function(data) {return function() {resume_click_event(data);}}
		            var hitCallback = null;
		            
				    while(ce = e_stack.pop())
				    {
						if (ce['link'].substr(0,10) === "javascript") {continue;}//if the link is javascript call ignore it
						hitCallback = middleMouse ? function(){} : callbackCreate(ce);
				    	//if a link with no event do nothing
					    if (ce['event'] == '') {hitCallback(); return true;}
						
				    					        window.ga('t0.send',{
                            'hitType': 'event',          
                            'eventCategory': 'side-box-events',
                            'eventAction': ce['event'], 
                            'eventValue' : 1,
                            'hitCallback': hitCallback //resume click event
				            }
				        );
				        //fallback if ga doesn't work
				        window.setTimeout(hitCallback,1500);
				    }
				    return middleMouse;
			    });
			    
			    //link event 
                _$b.on('mouseup','a',function(e){
					if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
                	e.preventDefault();
					var url = this.getAttribute('href');
					var event = this.getAttribute('data-gae');
					e_stack.push({'event':'','link':url});
					if (event)
					{
						e_stack.pop();
						e_stack.push({'event':event,'link':url});
					} 
				  });
    	        
		    })(id);
	    }		   	
	};
	
    var init = function()
    {
        if (disabled) {return;}
        if (typeof $ !== 'function') {return;}
        if (typeof ga !== 'function') {return;}
        register_events();
    }();
}(window.jQuery,window.ga,false);
</script>
<script>
	var marketLinksGA = function()
	{
		var createGAlinkEvent = function(linkLabel)
		{
			return function(e)
			{
				if (e.button === 2) {return true;} //right mouse button
				var middleMouse = e.button === 1;
				var enableCallback = true;
				var url = this.getAttribute('href');
				var callbackCreate = function(url) {return function() {window.location.href = url;};};
				var callback = function() {};
				
				enableCallback = this.hasAttribute('href') && !middleMouse;
				if (enableCallback) {e.preventDefault();}
				if (enableCallback) {callback = callbackCreate(url);}
				
				window.ga('t0.send',{
					'hitType': 'event',          
					'eventCategory': 'markets-links',
					'eventAction': 'click', 
					'eventLabel': linkLabel, 
					'eventValue' : 1,
					'hitCallback': callback
					}
				);
		
				//fallback incase google callback doesn't work
				window.setTimeout(callback,1500);
		
				return !enableCallback;
			};
		};
		
		var init = function()
		{
			//add action with google analytics
			$("#navRealTime > a").click(createGAlinkEvent('markets-top-navigation'));
			$("#markets_subnav_link").click(createGAlinkEvent('markets-popular'));
		}();

			$(document).ready(function (e) {
				var quotes = [
				'S&P 500','Nasdaq Composite','Gold','Crude Oil','EUR/USD','USD/JPY','US 10Y Yield',
				'EUR/USD 2nd','GBP/USD','USD/JPY 2nd','USD/CHF','AUD/USD','USD/CAD','BTC/USD',
				'Dow 30','S&P 500 2nd','Nasdaq 100','DAX','FTSE 100','Nikkei 225','Hang Seng'
				];

				$('.quotesBarContentCellTop').click(function (e) {
					e.preventDefault(); // redirect after the following code
					var reDirectUrl =$('a',this).attr('href');
					var ulIdx = $(this).closest('ul').index()-1;
					var liIdx = $(this).closest('li').index();
					var quoteIdx = ulIdx*7+liIdx;
					if (typeof ga) {
					ga('send', 'event', quotes[quoteIdx], 'Click', 'HP Quotes Bar'); // replace to ga after Netta's approval.

					}
					if(reDirectUrl && reDirectUrl.length){
					setTimeout(function (e) {location.href=reDirectUrl;return;}, 100);
					}
					return false;
				});
			});





			}();
</script>
